    This object stores an override of a given version in a configuration along the path specified by the path occurrence.

    Use the newBaselineConfigurationOverride static factory method(s), not the BaselineConfigurationOverride constructor, to construct instances of this class. Instances must be constructed using the static factory(s), in order to ensure proper initialization of the instance.
